      "content": "Intermittent \"Connection reset by peer\" errors can stem from various places. While security groups and NACLs can cause connection drops, this error often suggests the *remote* endpoint abruptly terminated the connection, pointing more towards an application or network intermediary issue. I recommend checking your application logs for timeouts or resource constraints first, as this is the most common source for this specific error.",
